Package game.consume

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ConsumeAction
    The ConsumeAction class represents an action where an actor consumes a consumable item.
    ConsumeItem
    The ConsumeItem class is an abstract class that represents an item that can be consumed in the game.
    EscapeRope
    The EscapeRope class represents an item called "Escape Rope" that can be consumed only once by actors in the game.
    FlaskOfCrimsonTears
    The FlaskOfCrimsonTears class represents a potion item called "Flask Of Crimson Tears" that can be consumed by actors in the game.
    GoldenRunes
    Golden Rune is an item that can be found in the ground.
    GoldenSeeds
    The GoldenSeeds class represents a consumable item called "Golden Seeds" in the game.
    PickUpConsumeItemAction
    A pick up action catered for consumable items.
